---

---

<section id="about" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <p class="section-number">About</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">A foundation in hardware-software integration, applied to AI.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>
          I graduated with a degree in <strong>Computer Engineering</strong> from the
          <strong>University of Indonesia</strong> (Class of 2018). Blending a strong
          foundation in hardware-software integration with modern software engineering,
          I specialize in bridging the gap between core backend systems and cutting-edge
          Artificial Intelligence.
        </p>
        <p>
          My work spans designing intelligent AI agents, building infrastructure automation
          tools, and architecting end-to-end systems for production AI workloads.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-cards">
        <div class="about-card glass">
          <p class="card-label">Education</p>
          <p class="card-value">B.Eng Computer Engineering</p>
          <p class="card-sub">Universitas Indonesia, 2018</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-card glass">
          <p class="card-label">Focus</p>
          <p class="card-value">AI Agents & Infrastructure</p>
          <p class="card-sub">Backend systems + AI integration</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xxl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .section-number {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.43;
    letter-spacing: -0.224px;
    color: var(--ink-muted-48);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .about-text p {
    color: var(--ink-muted-48);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.47;
    letter-spacing: -0.374px;
  }

  .about-text strong {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .about-cards {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .about-card {
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .card-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.12px;
    color: var(--ink-muted-48);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .card-value {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 17px;
    letter-spacing: -0.374px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xxs);
  }

  .card-sub {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.43;
    letter-spacing: -0.224px;
    color: var(--ink-muted-48);
  }
</style>
